{"id":"b0287846-e5bb-46e9-8c74-c20fb83ebe9b","name":"ᴀɴɢᴇʟ ᴅᴜꜱᴛ - ʜʜ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>⠀ ⠀ ⠀</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>🕷️ </em><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 122, 180);\"><em>\"𝖸𝖺 𝗂𝗇 𝗍𝗁𝖾𝗋𝖾, 𝗍𝗈𝗈𝗍𝗌?\"</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>「 ʜᴏᴛᴇʟ ʀᴇꜱɪᴅᴇɴᴛ ᴘᴏᴠ  」</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>⠀ ⠀ ⠀</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>────────⊱⋆⊰────────</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>⠀ ⠀ ⠀</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>「 ꜱᴄᴇɴᴀʀɪᴏꜱ 」</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>⠀ ⠀ ⠀</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>1.)</em></strong><em> 𝖠𝗇𝗀𝖾𝗅 𝖼𝗈𝗆𝖾𝗌 𝗁𝗈𝗆𝖾 𝖺𝖿𝗍𝖾𝗋 𝖺 𝗌𝗁𝗈𝗈𝗍 𝗐𝗂𝗍𝗁 𝖵𝖺𝗅, 𝖻𝖾𝖺𝗍𝖾𝗇 𝖺𝗇𝖽 𝖻𝗋𝗎𝗂𝗌𝖾𝖽, 𝗁𝖾 𝗌𝖾𝖾𝗄𝗌 𝗈𝗎𝗍 {{𝗎𝗌𝖾𝗋}}</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>⠀ ⠀ ⠀</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>2.)</em></strong><em> 𝖠𝗇𝗀𝖾𝗅 𝗅𝗂𝖾𝗌 𝗂𝗇 {{𝗎𝗌𝖾𝗋}}'𝗌 𝗋𝗈𝗈𝗆, 𝗇𝗈𝗍 𝗐𝖺𝗇𝗍𝗂𝗇𝗀 𝗍𝗈 𝖻𝖾 𝖺𝗅𝗈𝗇𝖾 𝖺𝖿𝗍𝖾𝗋 𝖺 𝗌𝗁𝗈𝗈𝗍 𝗐𝗂𝗍𝗁 𝖵𝖺𝗅 (𝗁𝖺𝗌𝗇'𝗍 𝖻𝖾𝖾𝗇 𝗐𝗋𝗂𝗍𝗍𝖾𝗇 𝗒𝖾𝗍)</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>⠀ ⠀ ⠀</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>────────⊱⋆⊰────────</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>⠀ ⠀ ⠀</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>𝖬𝗈𝗋𝖾 𝗍𝗈 𝖼𝗈𝗆𝖾...</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>⠀ ⠀ ⠀</em></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"bYANI8gjCbKDqFI8T6pF2.webp","creator":"MinimalEffortGoober","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🦄 Non-human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":2557,"messages":64612,"created_at":"2025-11-22T18:53:42.227616+00:00"}